{"tid":1656349,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"亞視前公關出戰灣仔","createTime":"2019-10-15T14:08:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T16:00:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ad35090015885f721ad046162d4a0812e0d009ca","tid":1656349,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T14:08:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20191015/20787335\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191015%2F20787335&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLLVsU2rIM%2B0kfQ6zMqXKyqM%3D&h=453c6d11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191015%2F20787335&h=7f3f5671\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20191015/20787335</a><br />\n<br />\n亞視前公關出戰灣仔<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191015/large/1571071804_72e4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191015%2Flarge%2F1571071804_72e4.gif&h=df95f076&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今年8月曾表示有意參加區議會選舉的黃夏蕙，日前突然在社交網宣佈放棄參選。不過，亞視前公關黃守東（圖）就一腔熱血，在昨日宣佈以獨立人士身份報名參選今年區議會選舉灣仔軒尼詩選區議席。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：長毛參戰阻李慧琼自動當選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「用大智慧謀出路」<br />\n<br />\n直至昨日，黃守東向傳媒發放新聞稿宣佈參選，並於報名前舉行造勢儀式，獲亞視一班舊同事包括葉家寶、魏秋樺、宮雪花、劉錫賢、筱靖、袁潔儀和黃竣鋒等到場支持，葉家寶等人送上一面「勝」字旗預祝「旗開得勝」。<br />\n<br />\n黃守東指自己跟灣仔區朋友接觸時，大家都記得當年他在亞視以發言人及對外事務主管身份處理停播危機，他亦會將這份堅毅精神來服務社區。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者聯絡黃守東，問他對於連月來反送中運動引發的警民衝突有何睇法，黃守東回應：「今天的局面需要有一些大智慧，在位者亦必須要用高度再高一點的大局觀去看整個局勢，謀求如何才能做出對香港最好的決定和事情，而非單單的你來我往式的矛盾和暴力，來加深我們社會的撕裂，希望我們的家人&mdash;&mdash;香港人，都用大智慧大局觀謀出路，香港人一同加油，讓我們的家園回復安寧、美麗如昔。」<br />\n<br />\n現時已報名參選同一選區的人士，包括「灣仔起步」組織的成員顧國慧，以及已向工黨申請凍結黨籍的夏希諾。 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n建制護航 陳健波續掌財委會<br />\n<br />\n長毛參戰阻李慧琼自動當選<br />\n學者籲如期區選免局勢升級<br />\n建制護航 陳健波續掌財委會<br />\n政府再質疑「自決」 鋪路DQ黃之鋒"},{"pid":"c3458777efead4e6951721420f77ee0c3108bacc","tid":1656349,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T14:09:42.000Z","msg":"有冇人識佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc4af42e8af4121a38eadb4b48b45dbf8e4d053c","tid":1656349,"uid":10322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T14:11:38.000Z","msg":"藍定黃？"},{"pid":"36ad2d7cd7613e45da330a4464d59aa34e834aa3","tid":1656349,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T14:12:23.000Z","msg":"人生困難模式"},{"pid":"6e58ffeee5fb6bfd64e39d7d4709d6efbda4881e","tid":1656349,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc4af42e8af4121a38eadb4b48b45dbf8e4d053c","tid":1656349,"uid":10322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T14:11:38.000Z","msg":"藍定黃？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T14:13:21.000Z","msg":"亞視係咪藍<br />\n長毛好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c7b9424c904e2b123b43bc03e81920bae9a1e0","tid":1656349,"uid":267932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc4af42e8af4121a38eadb4b48b45dbf8e4d053c","tid":1656349,"uid":10322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T14:11:38.000Z","msg":"藍定黃？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T14:14:37.000Z","msg":"睇呢個答法,我覺得係藍.<br />\n不過再聽多D, 睇定D先<br />\n<br />\n最後,不是行動post, 不推文回覆."},{"pid":"b9d0745d6e2419312aabaaff0134a30d63e33561","tid":1656349,"uid":227510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:00:57.000Z","msg":"黃守東藍架<br />\n唔好投佢啊<br />\n利申: 灣仔區選民<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ANOoFuw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FANOoFuw.jpg&h=c0bd1ccf&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n圖片來源: 網上圖片"}]}